Business Communication Software

This project aims to develop a comprehensive communication platform designed for businesses to improve internal communication and collaboration. It provides tools for teams to interact, share ideas, and manage communication seamlessly within a business environment.

 Key Features:

- Real-Time Messaging: Enables instant communication between team members through real-time chat. Messages are sent and received instantly using WebSocket technology.
- Private and Group Chats: Users can engage in private one-on-one conversations or participate in group chats tailored for specific teams or projects.
- Instant Notifications: Real-time notifications ensure users are immediately informed of new messages and updates.
- Message History: Users can access and search previous messages, making it easy to review past conversations and decisions.
- User-Friendly Interface: The platform offers a clean and intuitive chat interface that is easy to navigate and interact with.
